About



										Home
									


									 
								

									About
								










									Hundreds of millions of patients are affected by healthcare-associated
infections worldwide each year, leading to significant mortality and
financial losses for health systems.
Of every 100 hospitalized patients at any given time, 7 in developed and 10
in developing countries will acquire at least one healthcare-associated
infection. 
								

—  World Health Organization(WHO)



























												Welcome to NMI Health
											

												We are a healthcare product development and distribution company providing innovative and cost effective infection prevention medical textiles and fabrics to a variety of market segments within the health care industry. Supplied through our channel partnerships, our end customers range from hospitals, emergency services, surgery centers, long-term care facilities, nursing homes and other clinical settings throughout the healthcare continuum. 

Central to our company's performance and growth is our unique line of innovative antimicrobial fabrics called SilverCare Plus® co-branded and manufactured with X-Static® silver yarn. This unique technology has a layer of pure silver permanently bonded to the surface of a textile yarn that is woven into all our medical textiles. (See Technology Tab)

The silver yarn retains traditional textile and tactile characteristics, is inherent in all SilverCare Plus® fabrics and is active for the life of each product. An extensive range of SilverCare Plus® medical fabrics have been created for a variety of end uses within healthcare environments to reduce the threat of microbial sources. The fabrics within our product range are all re-useable, technologically advanced and lightweight; providing continuous, comprehensive and permanent 99.9% antimicrobial performance throughout the life of each fabric.
Today, the fundamental principles that guided the development of our medical textiles and fabrics remain a constant. They define our commitment to developing products that function the way they are intended, are manufactured to the very highest standards, achieve benchmark levels of performance, inspire confidence with their use,  protect the health of those who use them and ultimately save lives. The future holds promise as we continue to expand our channels of distribution, strengthen our relationship with our customers, and build our product portfolio with innovative and cost effective medical textiles and fabrics.  


Mission Statement



It is through our ongoing commitment to innovation and service, in making people's daily lives and work environments safer and healthier, that we will strive to build positive value, growth and returns for our investor

















