Healthcare Equipment and Supplies

Company Overview of NMI Health Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
NMI Health, Inc., a healthcare product development and distribution company, provides emergency and critical care, and infection control products to the healthcare industry. It offers antimicrobial hospital fabrics and textiles, including privacy curtains, lab coats, scrubs, gowns, bed linens, blankets, and additional barrier products to inhibit the growth of virus, fungi, and bacteria causing hospital acquired infections on healthcare apparel and textiles. NMI Health, Inc. offers its products under the SilverCare Plus name. The company was formerly known as Nano Mask, Inc. and changed its name to NMI Health, Inc. in June 2013. NMI Health, Inc. was founded in 1991 and is based in Reno, Nevad...
NMI Health, Inc., a healthcare product development and distribution company, provides emergency and critical care, and infection control products to the healthcare industry. It offers antimicrobial hospital fabrics and textiles, including privacy curtains, lab coats, scrubs, gowns, bed linens, blankets, and additional barrier products to inhibit the growth of virus, fungi, and bacteria causing hospital acquired infections on healthcare apparel and textiles. NMI Health, Inc. offers its products under the SilverCare Plus name. The company was formerly known as Nano Mask, Inc. and changed its name to NMI Health, Inc. in June 2013. NMI Health, Inc. was founded in 1991 and is based in Reno, Nevada.
