NMI Health Inc. Key Developments

NMI Health Inc. announced delayed annual 10-K filing
Apr 4 17
On 04/04/2017, NMI Health Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-K by the deadline required by the SEC.


NMI Health Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
Dec 9 16
On 12/09/2016, NMI Health Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


NMI Health Inc. Auditor Raises 'Going Concern' Doubt
Jun 8 16
NMI Health Inc. filed its 10-12G on Jun 08, 2016 for the period ending Dec 31, 2015. In this report its auditor, Malone & Bailey, PLLC, gave an unqualified opinion expressing doubt that the company can continue as a going concern.


