Company Profile
NMI Health, Inc. engages in healthcare product development and distribution. It provides emergency and critical care and infection control products. The firms products include privacy curtains, bed sheets, blankets, patient gowns, medical scrubs, and lab coats. It provides infection prevention products and solutions. The company was founded on November 1, 1991 and is headquartered in Reno, NV.








































