More from FactSet »










Description




NMI Health, Inc., formerly Nano Mask, Inc., is healthcare product development and distribution company. The Company is engaged in providing emergency and critical care and infection control products to a range of market segments within the healthcare industry. The Company offers antimicrobial performance based hospital fabrics and textiles to inhibit the growth of virus, fungi and bacteria causing hospital acquired infections (HAIs) on both healthcare apparel and textiles. The Company offers a line of antimicrobial fabrics called SilverCare Plus co-branded and are manufactured with X-Static silver yarn. The SilverCare Plus antimicrobial performance fabrics are specifically designed to reduce both soft surface contamination and lateral transmission of bacterial causing infections from and between patients, visitors and healthcare personnel. The Company offers products, such as medical scrubs, lab coats, patient gowns, privacy curtains, bed sheets and blankets.


